    <body>
        <pb n="1"/>
        <header>
            <ln n="1"/><date when="1929-12-17">1929-12-17</date>
            <ln n="2"/><greeting>Dear Warren-</greeting>
        </header>
        <p n="1">
            <ln n="1"/>Headed in
            <ln n="2"/><placeName placeId="NorthCarolina">Southern Pines</placeName>. Next day 
            <ln n="3"/>Charleston &amp; the <transport>Amida</transport> 
            <ln n="4"/>hill.WSwonderful to see
            <ln n="5"/><unclear reason="not sure">for it.</unclear> <unclear reason="not sure">O all </unclear>
            <ln n="6"/>&amp; gather for Christmas.
            <ln n="7"/>We telephoned <persName>Betty</persName>&amp;
            <ln n="8"/><underline>offically</underline> invite her -and
            <ln n="9"/>she says she is coming
            <ln n="10"/><unclear reason="not sure">lawnell 27.?.</unclear> Possibly
            <ln n="11"/>you have heard were
            <ln n="12"/>about this. Much love
            <ln n="13"/>think of how much
            <ln n="14"/>we care for you and
            <!-- ged: start of 2 page -->
            <pb n="2"/>
            <ln n="15"/><unclear reason="no idea">found</unclear> with due <unclear reason="no idea">caution</unclear> <!-- seb: i believe the first word in this line is "Proceed -->
            <ln n="16"/>Lot of wild drivers on 
            <ln n="17"/>the road 
            <closer> 
                <ln n="18" />M. Warren.
            </closer>
        </p>
        <p n="2"> <!-- am: Fathers letter on the back of the page-->
            <ln n="1"/><transport>Duesenberg</transport> ran beautifully -so far!
            <ln n="2"/>First day <weather>nice weather</weather>; <underline>very</underline> cold
            <ln n="3"/>yesterday. You may need your coon
            <ln n="4"/><object>coat</object>, heavy <object>hat</object> or fur <object>cap</object>!!
            <ln n="5"/>Look forward to our Wiedersehen. <!-- ged: This is German for meet again --> 
        </p>    
        <closer>
            <ln n="1"/>Faithfully
            <ln n="2"/>Father.
        </closer>
    </body>
